The dataset files in this directory are dedicated to the public domain under
Creative Commons CC0 1.0. To the extent possible under law, Zip-Codes.com has
waived all copyright and related or neighboring rights to these dataset files.

Full text: https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/legalcode

The underlying source data is the U.S. Census Bureau American Community Survey
(ACS) 5-Year Estimates, which is itself in the public domain as a work of the
U.S. federal government. This dedication covers the compiled, reshaped CSV
representation in this directory.

Suggested (not required) acknowledgement:

  Demographic data: US Census Bureau ACS 5-Year Estimates, accessed via
  ZIP Codes API (Zip-Codes.com), https://api.zip-codes.com
